data.description:
Nestled in the prestigious Cape Fear Crossing Community! This residence boasts a grand foyer and an inviting open-concept floorplan. The stunning kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring a large island, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample pantry storage. Spacious living room, complete with a cozy gas fireplace, seamlessly flowing into the formal dining area, providing a perfect setting for memorable gatherings.The primary suite exudes elegance with its trey ceilings, luxurious jetted tub, separate shower, dual vanity, and an oversized walk-in closet. Upstairs, you'll find a bright and inviting space with four generously-sized bedrooms, two more full baths, a relaxing sitting area, and extra open attic storage.
Step outside to the rear of the home, where you'll be delighted by the covered porch, fully fenced backyard, and plenty of space for a future pool, offering endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment. The HVAC system was newly installed.
